### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5005
@model = deepseek-ocr
@prompt = Extract the text in the image.
@stream = false
@userId = 42212628-cddd-4d28-972f-8336492a9d99
@username = saad alsaree
@userLogin = 101313
@fullName = saad alsaree
@email = saad@mail.com
@organizationalUnitId = a2e50645-97cb-41cf-8d23-6b669aea3bc6
@image1 = 
@image2 = 

### ملاحظة:
### ضع base64 string للصورة في @image1 أو @image2
### يمكنك تغيير @model إلى أي موديل OCR متاح
### يمكنك تغيير @prompt حسب الحاجة
### يمكنك تغيير @stream إلى true لتفعيل الستريمنج أو false لإلغائه
### بيانات المستخدم مطلوبة في body الطلب

### OCR - Non-Streaming (صورة واحدة)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ocr
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "{{model}}",
  "prompt": "{{prompt}}",
  "images": ["{{image1}}"],
  "stream": {{stream}},
  "id": "{{userId}}",
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "userLogin": "{{userLogin}}",
  "fullName": "{{fullName}}",
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "organizationalUnitId": "{{organizationalUnitId}}"
}

### OCR - Streaming (صورة واحدة)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ocr
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "{{model}}",
  "prompt": "{{prompt}}",
  "images": ["{{image1}}"],
  "stream": true,
  "id": "{{userId}}",
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "userLogin": "{{userLogin}}",
  "fullName": "{{fullName}}",
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "organizationalUnitId": "{{organizationalUnitId}}"
}

### OCR - Multiple Images (صور متعددة)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ocr
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "{{model}}",
  "prompt": "{{prompt}}",
  "images": ["{{image1}}", "{{image2}}"],
  "stream": {{stream}},
  "id": "{{userId}}",
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "userLogin": "{{userLogin}}",
  "fullName": "{{fullName}}",
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "organizationalUnitId": "{{organizationalUnitId}}"
}

### OCR - Error Test (Missing Images)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ocr
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "{{model}}",
  "prompt": "{{prompt}}",
  "images": [],
  "stream": {{stream}},
  "id": "{{userId}}",
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "userLogin": "{{userLogin}}",
  "fullName": "{{fullName}}",
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "organizationalUnitId": "{{organizationalUnitId}}"
}

### OCR - Error Test (Missing Model)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ocr
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "{{prompt}}",
  "images": ["{{image1}}"],
  "stream": {{stream}},
  "id": "{{userId}}",
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "userLogin": "{{userLogin}}",
  "fullName": "{{fullName}}",
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "organizationalUnitId": "{{organizationalUnitId}}"
}

